        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued June 15 at 2:27AM MDT until June 15 at 3:00AM MDT by NWS Glasgow MT</headline>
        <description>At 226 AM MDT, a severe thunderstorm was located 10 miles southwest
of Vida, or 21 miles north of Circle, moving east at 25 mph.

HAZARD...Quarter size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Damage to vehicles is expected.

Locations impacted include...
Vida, Weldon, and Nelson Creek Rec Area.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.

Torrential rainfall is occurring with this storm, which may lead to
ponding on area roadways.</instruction>
